snippet.title: Smackdown! 2: Shock Value (Teaser Trailer)
snippet.description:
Smackdown! Shock Value is a modding project created by a team led by NMCM, longtime smackdown modder in collaboration with Code Nekomancer & Kendrick SD2.

We use retroarch and hard in-rom modding to achieve several different results in terms of visuals and gameplay. This trailer showcases the changes to the visuals through highlights matches played within the game. We're planning to release a mostly up to date roster and also reward our supporters with several different benefits.

Support us and follow us on other social media!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/NMCM_SD2LeGeNd
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/code_NKMNCR
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/NMCM/
LIVE STREAMS: https://www.twitch.tv/platinum_nmcm
REDDIT: https://www.reddit.com/user/NMCM_SD2LeGeNd

Original Trailer by Code_NKMNCR
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyU1um9j-Gng6FkQPEOmXng


Thank you so much for your attention, interest and support. We're working hard to give you the best result we can possibly achieve!


#Wrestling #Videogames #NMCM #Smackdown #Classic #Mod #newlegacyinc #SD2 #smackdown2 #yumboy11
